MSI_Validation.Name: Post-processing by ProteoRed MIAPE Extractor tool
MSI_Validation.GlobalThresholds: FDR at 1.0% at protein level in 'rep:3' (Mascot:score)

userParam.name: The ProteoRed MIAPE Extractor tool is a standalone tool that allows: to obtain graphical representations of qualitative information from MIAPE MSI documents; to automatically create MIAPE compliant reports from your standard data files (PRIDE XML, mzML, mzIdentML) and others (XTandem output xml), storing these reports in the ProteoRed MIAPE repository; to export your MIAPE-compliant reports to standard data files (currently to PRIDE XML).

MSI_PostProcessing_Software.Parameters: Mascot:SigThreshold=0.05 Mascot:MaxProteinHits=Auto Mascot:ProteinScoringMethod=MudPIT Mascot:MinMSMSThreshold=0 Mascot:ShowHomologousProteinsWithSamePeptides=1 Mascot:ShowHomologousProteinsWithSubsetOfPeptides=10 Mascot:RequireBoldRed=0 Mascot:UseUnigeneClustering=false Mascot:IncludeErrorTolerantMatches=1 Mascot:ShowDecoyMatches=0 no threshold
